Physiology MBT     Biomedical Implants  Materials  Design  Characterization and Clinical Safety MBT     Introduction to Flow Cytometry and Confocal Microscopy MBT     Stem Cells and Regenerative Engineering MBT     Lab Animal  Use and Care MBT     Immunoassay Development MBT     Advance Protein Biochemistry MBT     Departmental Seminar in Medical Biotechnology MBT     Internship in Medical Biotechnology MBT     Special Topics in Biotechnology MBT     Independent Study Course Structure Requirement Research Track Option    coursework Option    internship Core courses    Credits Electives   Credits    Credits   Credits Research Project   Credits n a n a     hours     weeks  FT Total credits    Credits    Credits    Credits Below is a typical   year structure that can be followed by all full time students beginning their program during the Fall semester Fall Spring CORE COURSES Biostatistics Protein Biochemistry Bioethics Student Seminar in Med  Biotech Biotech Product Development RESEARCH TRACK     INTERNSHIP TRACK Internship in Med Biotech Internship in Med Biotech About Education Research Patient Care Departments News Giving INFORMATION FOR  Prospective and Current Students Faculty   Staff Alumni   Friends Patients Businesses and Community RESOURCES  UIC Directory Blackboard Emergency Information Contact Us Apply Now Give Contact Us If you have questions  comments  or problems accessing this site  please E mail the webmaster College of Medicine Chicago Peoria Rockford Urbana 